{"sha": "3419e20f3b0800d40a4e33d47da7051d142e62ce", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOjM0MTllMjBmM2IwODAwZDQwYTRlMzNkNDdkYTcwNTFkMTQyZTYyY2U=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Alex Crichton", "email": "alex@alexcrichton.com", "date": "2014-07-18T14:24:28Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Alex Crichton", "email": "alex@alexcrichton.com", "date": "2014-07-18T14:26:55Z"}, "message": "sync: Fail with init semaphore count < 0\n\nSemaphores are not currently designed to handle this case correctly, leading to\nvery strange behavior. Semaphores as written are intended to count *resources*\nand it's not possible to have a negative number of resources.\n\nThis alters the behavior and documentation to note that the task will be failed\nif the initial count is 0.\n\nCloses #15758", "tree": {"sha": "093da0d6f7dc5f9bd534ac34556e350a3ac078db", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/093da0d6f7dc5f9bd534ac34556e350a3ac078db"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/3419e20f3b0800d40a4e33d47da7051d142e62ce", "comment_count": 5, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/3419e20f3b0800d40a4e33d47da7051d142e62ce", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/3419e20f3b0800d40a4e33d47da7051d142e62ce", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/3419e20f3b0800d40a4e33d47da7051d142e62ce/comments", "author": {"login": "alexcrichton", "id": 64996, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY0OTk2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/64996?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton", "html_url": "https://github.com/alexcrichton", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https: